Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:34.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}I find you there so happy in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:43.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}闇の中1人で　the sky parade is calling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:49.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}So come along　見つけ出して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:59.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}波が高く　the tide will come
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:04.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}約束する　make you smile
