Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:16.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}The times you held yourself and cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:20.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}この世界と一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.67,0:23:24.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}Taking that road from a beast to a God
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:31.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\blur2}いつか　you'll be above the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:24.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}在此駐足 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.49,0:22:28.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}閉上雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:34.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}如此幸運 能在黑暗中遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:43.13,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}在黑暗中孤身一人 那天空中的遊行彷彿正呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:49.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}所以 啟程吧 找到它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:59.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}浪濤洶湧 時機將至
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:04.94,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}與你相約 予你笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:08.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}大步向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:16.37,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}無論駐足多少次 哭泣了多少眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:20.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}與這世界一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.67,0:23:24.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}在蛻變的道路上不斷前行
